    ConstraintFactory
    The ConstraintFactory class represents the Factory Method Pattern for generating and mapping ConstraintTemplate classes the set of constraint formats that can be used to describe the desired synthesis output.
    ConstraintTemplate
    The ConstraintTemplate class is an abstract class used to represent a general constraint template.
